msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werebear.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 10 in humanoid form, 11 (natural armor) in bear and hybrid "
"form    \n"
"**Hit Points** 135 (18d8 + 54)    \n"
"**Speed** 30 ft. (40 ft., climb 30 ft. in bear or hybrid form) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werebear.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 19 (+4) | 10 (+0) | 17 (+3) | 11 (+0) | 12 (+1) | 12 (+1) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werebear.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Perception +7    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical "
"attacks not made with silvered weapons    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 17    \n"
"**Languages** Common (can't speak in bear form)    \n"
"**Challenge** 5 (1,800 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werebear.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Shapechanger.** The werebear can use its action to polymorph into a Large "
"bear-humanoid hybrid or into a Large bear, or back into its true form, which "
"is humanoid. Its statistics, other than its size and AC, are the same in "
"each form. Any equipment it is wearing or carrying isn't transformed. It "
"reverts to its true form if it dies.    \n"
"**Keen Smell.** The werebear has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks "
"that rely on smell. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/werebear.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** In bear form, the werebear makes two claw attacks. In "
"humanoid form, it makes two greataxe attacks. In hybrid form, it can attack "
"like a bear or a humanoid.    \n"
"**Bite (Bear or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, reach "
"5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 15 (2d10 + 4) piercing damage. If the target is a "
"humanoid, it must succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or be cursed "
"with werebear lycanthropy.    \n"
"**Claw (Bear or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, reach "
"5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 13 (2d8 + 4) slashing damage.    \n"
"**Greataxe (Humanoid or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to "
"hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 10 (1d12 + 4) slashing damage.\n"
msgstr ""
